lenders.occupational_info:
I am currently a full time student in college, and I am almost ready to attend university. I am studying Computer Science to learn how to write software for computers, and build and operate websites and systems.

During the summer I built a website to give individuals better access to very short term online work "tasks." I evaluated the data I collected from users over a 4 month period and was amazed to find that 80% of the workers who participated were from India, Pakistan, Africa (in general), and other regions of similar economic status. During the existence of the website I was able to pay out nearly $10,000 to individuals. The realization that the short term work I provided ended up being outsourced to countries where the pay seemed much more competitive really excited me about the opportunities for offering work to individuals around the world. It is my hope, and my desire to continue this research and eventually create a website which combines what I've learned in a way that helps people find outsourced work.

lenders.occupational_info:
Have you ever felt that your Bank, Financial Adviser or Wealth Manager cares more about their relationship with your money, than their relationship with you? 

As I Financial Life Planner, I believe that 80% of the advice process is about YOU, and only 20% about your money, as a tool to help you live a truly fulfilling life. Your dreams, desires and aspirations are the core to your Financial Life Plan, and we help deliver them.

Bluecoat Wealth Management, a boutique financial planning business dedicated to providing independent advice and Financial Life Planning to individuals based in Sussex.

Bluecoat is founded on old school values - we operate a policy of working with a select number of clients, pre and post retirement, with whom we build strong long-term relationships and deliver a consistently high level of service.

We also believe in giving back to the community. We arecommitted to leaving a corporate legacy, applying the same principles as the legacy planning service we provide for our clients.
